1
00:00:06,718 --> 00:00:11,155
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,223 --> 00:00:14,750
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,826 --> 00:00:18,262
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,330 --> 00:00:21,925
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,265
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,337 --> 00:00:27,271
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,074 --> 00:00:32,009
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,077 --> 00:00:35,877
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,281 --> 00:00:43,119
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,355 --> 00:00:50,420
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,729 --> 00:00:56,861
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,002 --> 00:01:01,268
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:04,935
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,010 --> 00:01:08,343
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,413 --> 00:01:12,042
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,117 --> 00:01:15,712
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,787 --> 00:01:19,279
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,358 --> 00:01:22,816
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,028 --> 00:01:27,124
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:43,726 --> 00:01:46,320
My body movements
have finally returned...

21
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:48,660
<i>Blood...</i>

22
00:01:55,071 --> 00:01:56,003
Lady Tsunade!

23
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:01,901
Say! Say! What's happening?!

24
00:02:02,278 --> 00:02:04,940
Why's Kabuto fighting
with Old Lady Tsunade?!

25
00:02:05,915 --> 00:02:08,145
Take a good look at the headband!

26
00:02:09,485 --> 00:02:11,544
He's Orochimaru's subordinate.

27
00:02:13,856 --> 00:02:20,728
<i>Attack! Fury of the Rasengan!</i>

28
00:02:31,207 --> 00:02:32,902
That man is Orochimaru...

29
00:02:33,776 --> 00:02:36,472
Shizune, you take care of
the guy with the glasses...

30
00:02:37,113 --> 00:02:39,513
I'll take care of Orochimaru.

31
00:02:42,585 --> 00:02:48,421
Before that, I'd like to have Tsunade
do something about this body.

32
00:02:48,691 --> 00:02:52,422
The effects of that drug
might still last for awhile...

33
00:02:52,695 --> 00:02:54,925
There's nothing that
I can do about it.

34
00:02:54,997 --> 00:02:56,965
What? Really?

35
00:02:57,633 --> 00:02:59,624
Geez. I guess it can't be helped.

36
00:03:00,369 --> 00:03:02,564
I have no choice
but to fight in this condition.

37
00:03:03,506 --> 00:03:07,465
Tsunade... Rest your body
with Recovery Ninjutsu.

38
00:03:07,676 --> 00:03:09,644
Then... What about me, me?

39
00:03:09,812 --> 00:03:14,112
You guard Tsunade together
with that pig.

40
00:03:14,917 --> 00:03:18,478
What?! I want to fight, too.
Even I can...

41
00:03:18,554 --> 00:03:19,612
No, you won't!

42
00:03:20,022 --> 00:03:21,887
Like that four-eyed kid said, right?

43
00:03:22,625 --> 00:03:23,956
You're on a different level.

44
00:03:25,194 --> 00:03:27,958
The opponent is a Sannin like myself,

45
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:29,964
and the man who killed
the Third Hokage

46
00:03:30,933 --> 00:03:35,495
An eye for an eye...
I'm the only one who can fight him.

47
00:03:36,372 --> 00:03:40,638
And that four-eyed guy possesses
the same level of power as Kakashi.

48
00:03:42,111 --> 00:03:43,009
Okay.

49
00:03:43,612 --> 00:03:45,273
Then... Shadow Clo

50
00:03:45,347 --> 00:03:46,177
Hold it!

51
00:03:46,782 --> 00:03:50,775
Don't use the Shadow Clone Jutsu.
It'd be utterly pointless.

52
00:03:50,953 --> 00:03:51,817
What?

53
00:03:52,922 --> 00:03:55,083
It wouldn't even become
much of a diversion...

54
00:03:55,825 --> 00:03:57,918
It'd be a waste of Chakra...

55
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:02,821
with them as opponents.

56
00:04:05,601 --> 00:04:08,695
Now then, let's get this thing started.

57
00:04:19,849 --> 00:04:21,510
- Summoning Jutsu.
- Summoning Jutsu.

58
00:04:39,835 --> 00:04:40,767
Hi.

59
00:04:41,303 --> 00:04:43,328
- Huh?!
- What is this?!

60
00:04:43,572 --> 00:04:45,096
- Wha?!
- What the heck's going on?!

61
00:04:45,407 --> 00:04:46,874
Long time no see.

62
00:04:47,476 --> 00:04:48,534
<i>On account of the drug,</i>

63
00:04:48,611 --> 00:04:51,546
<i>Master Jiraiya still can't build up</i>
<i>Chakra very well.</i>

64
00:04:54,183 --> 00:04:57,914
It looks like your stupid
still hasn't healed, eh, Jiraiya.

65
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:02,848
That's too much even for you
with no ability.

66
00:05:03,859 --> 00:05:06,851
It seems Tsunade got you
with something.

67
00:05:07,396 --> 00:05:10,126
A sacrifice was necessary for that Jutsu,

68
00:05:10,699 --> 00:05:13,293
so perhaps she was thinking ahead
and drugged him

69
00:05:13,369 --> 00:05:15,837
with something that
would contain his power.

70
00:05:16,772 --> 00:05:19,798
To think she'd make
a sacrifice of Jiraiya...

71
00:05:20,242 --> 00:05:24,201
Well, it sounds just like Tsunade.

72
00:05:25,781 --> 00:05:28,807
<i>To think I'd already have</i>
<i>my handicap spotted.</i>

73
00:05:30,986 --> 00:05:34,217
You are such
a disgraceful guy as always...

74
00:05:35,090 --> 00:05:39,857
<i>Dang it. It kind of ticks me off</i>
<i>when the Pervy Sage is mocked.</i>

75
00:05:41,764 --> 00:05:43,061
Summoning... Jutsu!

76
00:05:46,368 --> 00:05:49,531
The Nine Tailed Fox kid
from the Chunin Exam.

77
00:05:50,072 --> 00:05:53,473
I wonder if I should've killed him then,
after all.

78
00:05:54,143 --> 00:05:56,805
For the sake of the Akatsuki organization,

79
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:59,245
I acknowledged his achievement...
and let him slide by.

80
00:06:00,115 --> 00:06:03,050
But the only ones who can break
a Five-Pronged Spell

81
00:06:03,285 --> 00:06:06,812
are the Sannin members
and the Third Hokage.

82
00:06:07,256 --> 00:06:10,555
Which means Jiraiya may have
already taught it to Naruto.

83
00:06:11,794 --> 00:06:13,125
Perhaps.

84
00:06:13,629 --> 00:06:17,656
If he's able to control
the Nine Tailed Fox's power...

85
00:06:19,435 --> 00:06:20,868
Oh...

86
00:06:21,303 --> 00:06:22,793
Th-This is...

87
00:06:27,843 --> 00:06:30,004
It doesn't quite look to be so.

88
00:06:32,381 --> 00:06:36,181
He isn't endowed with Shinobi ability
to begin with, so...

89
00:06:37,186 --> 00:06:38,244
Why?

90
00:06:41,223 --> 00:06:43,691
<i>He's still got a long way to go,</i>
<i>sure enough.</i>

91
00:06:44,893 --> 00:06:46,884
Why?!

92
00:06:48,731 --> 00:06:50,665
Hello.

93
00:06:54,203 --> 00:06:58,333
Hey, Gamatatsu.
Why did you come out?

94
00:07:00,175 --> 00:07:03,076
Oh, Brother Gamakichi.

95
00:07:03,679 --> 00:07:06,113
It's the first time I've been Summoned.

96
00:07:06,181 --> 00:07:08,308
I-I wonder if I can do my best?

97
00:07:08,851 --> 00:07:12,582
Idiot. Get some snacks
or something and hide.

98
00:07:12,888 --> 00:07:17,552
What? I can get snacks?
Goody goody.

99
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:18,949
Here I go.

100
00:07:21,997 --> 00:07:23,624
I'll take Jiraiya.

101
00:07:24,366 --> 00:07:26,834
I leave the rest to you.

102
00:07:27,503 --> 00:07:28,765
It's unfortunate...

103
00:07:29,371 --> 00:07:33,034
Here I also wanted to fight Lord Jiraiya,
one of the Sannin.

104
00:07:57,499 --> 00:07:58,761
Naruto!

105
00:08:00,135 --> 00:08:02,365
Your opponent is me.

106
00:08:07,009 --> 00:08:08,840
Earth Style! Dark Swamp!

107
00:08:19,154 --> 00:08:24,217
Dang it. I can't completely sink them
with such a puny swamp.

108
00:08:25,127 --> 00:08:27,095
<i>The drug is still working.</i>

109
00:08:28,130 --> 00:08:31,998
But... with this, the snakes can't move.

110
00:08:42,010 --> 00:08:43,910
<i>Ninja Art! Poison Fog!</i>

111
00:08:46,915 --> 00:08:48,542
<i>I'll be up a creek if</i>
<i>I take even one breath.</i>

112
00:09:01,563 --> 00:09:02,894
My leg tendons...!

113
00:09:09,304 --> 00:09:12,068
I won't be eaten twice...!
No way!

114
00:09:28,657 --> 00:09:29,749
Here I go.

115
00:09:35,464 --> 00:09:38,399
Ninja Art! Needle Jizo!

116
00:09:43,172 --> 00:09:46,437
<i>Dang it...The Jutsu isn't working well.</i>

117
00:09:47,409 --> 00:09:51,539
Even if we both have handicaps,
you won't one up me...

118
00:09:51,847 --> 00:09:53,974
Give up now.

119
00:10:31,453 --> 00:10:32,579
It's unfortunate...

120
00:10:33,021 --> 00:10:36,787
Here I had respected you
as a fellow Medical Ninja.

121
00:10:37,092 --> 00:10:39,424
Stop. Stay back!

122
00:10:39,661 --> 00:10:42,095
Please hang on, Lady Tsunade...

123
00:10:42,898 --> 00:10:48,336
The Sannin name, which Lord Orochimaru
is also called, will cry.

124
00:10:53,609 --> 00:10:55,600
My body's heavy.

125
00:10:58,747 --> 00:11:02,774
To think you who were
once called the village madness

126
00:11:02,851 --> 00:11:07,584
would ferry around such a kid
and struggle tirelessly for the village.

127
00:11:07,656 --> 00:11:09,317
You've really fallen, haven't you?

128
00:11:09,391 --> 00:11:14,454
I have a keen eye to discern ability.

129
00:11:16,064 --> 00:11:21,502
And that kid... is mediocrity in my eyes.

130
00:11:22,738 --> 00:11:27,937
It's precisely for this reason...
that I don't need the Uchiha kid.

131
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:33,443
It's no fun raising a genius
who's good from the start.

132
00:11:35,217 --> 00:11:37,515
So you can't leave him alone

133
00:11:37,586 --> 00:11:39,713
because it's like you're looking
at your old self?

134
00:11:40,355 --> 00:11:47,227
That kid can't beat Uchiha who inherited
the inherent Sharingan Shinobi skill.

135
00:11:47,763 --> 00:11:51,927
And that's because Naruto
doesn't possess the Sharingan.

136
00:11:52,234 --> 00:11:54,065
Shinobi ability is about whether

137
00:11:54,136 --> 00:12:00,041
one can use and master
all the Jutsu of the world.

138
00:12:00,542 --> 00:12:05,844
Ninja refers to one
who can use Ninjutsu.

139
00:12:08,951 --> 00:12:12,318
Shinobi ability is no such thing.

140
00:12:13,555 --> 00:12:15,386
You still don't get it?

141
00:12:16,692 --> 00:12:21,459
A Ninja... is one who endures.

142
00:12:22,931 --> 00:12:24,796
It's a difference of opinion, huh.

143
00:12:26,201 --> 00:12:28,829
I'll teach you one thing.

144
00:12:29,871 --> 00:12:33,398
What's most important for Shinobi ability...

145
00:12:34,042 --> 00:12:37,341
isn't the number of Jutsu
one possesses.

146
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:40,073
What's important is...

147
00:12:42,317 --> 00:12:44,114
The mettle...

148
00:12:44,186 --> 00:12:46,882
not to give up.

149
00:12:57,033 --> 00:13:00,025
Enough already... you jerk!

150
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:17,083
The mettle to never give up...

151
00:13:18,321 --> 00:13:20,482
He possesses that.

152
00:13:40,243 --> 00:13:43,337
<i>Heh. I don't know what Jutsu you learned,</i>

153
00:13:43,646 --> 00:13:47,013
<i>but you can't hit me with</i>
<i>such a large motion.</i>

154
00:13:49,318 --> 00:13:50,546
<i>No good.</i>

155
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:53,316
<i>It won't easily hit with</i>
<i>a moving opponent.</i>

156
00:13:57,426 --> 00:13:59,155
Owwee!

157
00:14:00,363 --> 00:14:03,799
<i>And the Chakra isn't</i>
<i>completely held, yet...</i>

158
00:14:04,567 --> 00:14:07,627
It seems you got a cracked thigh bone
in your left leg

159
00:14:07,703 --> 00:14:09,967
from the battle with the snake.

160
00:14:11,207 --> 00:14:14,040
Well, you can still move if
it's just the bone.

161
00:14:15,077 --> 00:14:16,339
But it's impossible now...

162
00:14:17,346 --> 00:14:20,543
The lateral vastus muscle
in your right leg is totally cut off.

163
00:14:22,218 --> 00:14:24,345
<i>What should I do...?</i>

164
00:14:24,487 --> 00:14:27,183
<i>That Jutsu of mine uses both hands.</i>

165
00:14:27,256 --> 00:14:29,383
<i>If even one arm is taken out, it's over.</i>

166
00:14:32,862 --> 00:14:35,422
Are you scared of me?

167
00:14:35,865 --> 00:14:37,730
Do you want to run away from here?

168
00:14:42,505 --> 00:14:45,133
Naruto, as I recall,

169
00:14:45,207 --> 00:14:48,506
you whooped it up like this
during the first Chunin Exam.

170
00:14:49,845 --> 00:14:52,678
<i>Don't mess with me. I won't run away!</i>

171
00:14:55,251 --> 00:14:58,345
"Don't mess with me. I won't run away."

172
00:14:58,821 --> 00:15:02,484
"I'll take it. Even if I'm a Genin for life..."

173
00:15:02,558 --> 00:15:06,221
"I'll become the Hokage at any cost,
so it's okay with me."

174
00:15:06,629 --> 00:15:07,994
"I'm not scared."

175
00:15:08,998 --> 00:15:11,728
Can you...
whoop it up in the same way now?

176
00:15:14,270 --> 00:15:15,498
<i>Unlike you...</i>

177
00:15:15,571 --> 00:15:20,099
<i>I will be the heir to the Hokage name</i>
<i>no matter what!</i>

178
00:15:23,446 --> 00:15:25,914
- <i>Hokage is my dream!</i>
- <i>Hokage is my dream!</i>

179
00:15:29,585 --> 00:15:33,715
You're not a kid anymore,
so you should stop whooping it up...

180
00:15:34,357 --> 00:15:35,551
Depending on the situation,

181
00:15:35,624 --> 00:15:38,718
when you want to give up and run away,
you should run away.

182
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:47,767
Oh my... What's with that look?

183
00:15:48,504 --> 00:15:52,031
You'll die! If you die,
there are no dreams or anything...

184
00:15:55,511 --> 00:15:56,910
<i>Do you want to die?</i>

185
00:15:57,413 --> 00:16:01,907
<i>You're still a Genin,</i>
<i>so you should run away on the battlefield.</i>

186
00:16:02,752 --> 00:16:05,448
<i>Don't tell a man to run away.</i>

187
00:16:30,579 --> 00:16:33,241
Kids think that everything is easy.

188
00:16:34,050 --> 00:16:37,679
That's why they talk about foolish dreams
like nothing at all.

189
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:40,115
That's why they can't give up.

190
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:55,634
<i>Jiraiya, was it you</i>
<i>who taught him that Rasengan?</i>

191
00:16:56,405 --> 00:17:00,535
<i>Are you acting like a teacher by teaching</i>
<i>a Jutsu that can't be learned?</i>

192
00:17:00,876 --> 00:17:02,571
<i>Don't give him false hopes.</i>

193
00:17:03,145 --> 00:17:08,583
<i>That's why a moony kid starts joking</i>
<i>that he'll become the Hokage!</i>

194
00:17:15,624 --> 00:17:19,116
They chase after foolish dreams...
and then die.

195
00:17:19,829 --> 00:17:23,060
<i>If I have three days,</i>
<i>I'll master that Jutsu.</i>

196
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,991
<i>Then let's make a bet.</i>

197
00:17:37,313 --> 00:17:39,213
Bastard!

198
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:45,709
As for me... I stand by my words.

199
00:17:47,523 --> 00:17:51,357
That's... my Way of Ninja!

200
00:17:57,066 --> 00:17:58,090
<i>A bet?</i>

201
00:17:58,767 --> 00:18:00,166
<i>I'll give you one week.</i>

202
00:18:00,636 --> 00:18:03,127
<i>If you can master that Jutsu,</i>

203
00:18:03,506 --> 00:18:06,339
<i>I'll acknowledge that</i>
<i>you'll be able to become the Hokage...</i>

204
00:18:06,509 --> 00:18:08,670
<i>and give you this necklace.</i>

205
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,880
You should've just
stayed out of this...

206
00:18:22,691 --> 00:18:23,623
Why?

207
00:18:31,901 --> 00:18:32,925
Why?!

208
00:18:47,416 --> 00:18:49,680
Old Lady Tsunade...

209
00:18:53,656 --> 00:18:54,850
You're still going to get up?

210
00:18:59,261 --> 00:19:01,286
Just like our wager

211
00:19:01,363 --> 00:19:05,356
I will definitely win
that unlucky necklace from you.

212
00:19:08,637 --> 00:19:10,298
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

213
00:19:12,374 --> 00:19:14,137
<i>Shadow Clone won't do anything now.</i>

214
00:19:16,078 --> 00:19:20,105
Enough... Don't protect me, Naruto.
Stop it!

215
00:19:23,085 --> 00:19:26,384
I told you that you'd die
if you were obstinate like that, right?

216
00:19:26,855 --> 00:19:30,416
If you die, there will be no dreams,
no nothing.

217
00:19:30,492 --> 00:19:33,427
Just get out of the way. Run away.

218
00:19:35,097 --> 00:19:37,930
Humph... It's okay.

219
00:19:47,276 --> 00:19:48,265
I...

220
00:19:55,751 --> 00:19:57,912
I absolutely will not die...

221
00:19:58,354 --> 00:20:00,686
until I become the Hokage!

222
00:20:13,869 --> 00:20:16,565
This way, I can hold on to you.
Here I go!

223
00:20:23,579 --> 00:20:25,570
It's the same Chakra movement
as before.

224
00:20:26,548 --> 00:20:29,108
<i>No, this is...different.</i>

225
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:31,816
I see.

226
00:20:33,122 --> 00:20:35,283
In order to gain a hand
for suppressing Chakra,

227
00:20:35,724 --> 00:20:36,748
the Shadow Clone...

228
00:20:38,727 --> 00:20:40,592
Compress Chakra and...

229
00:20:42,031 --> 00:20:43,225
hold it completely.

230
00:20:46,669 --> 00:20:47,328
Wha?!

231
00:20:47,703 --> 00:20:49,000
I-It can't be.

232
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:52,200
Rasengan!

233
00:21:05,655 --> 00:21:10,354
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

234
00:21:10,426 --> 00:21:14,760
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

235
00:21:15,364 --> 00:21:18,891
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

236
00:21:20,136 --> 00:21:24,596
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

237
00:21:24,774 --> 00:21:30,212
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

238
00:21:30,713 --> 00:21:35,013
<i>That hold us together</i>

239
00:21:35,485 --> 00:21:44,723
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

240
00:21:44,794 --> 00:21:47,388
<i>you say laughingly</i>

241
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:53,296
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

242
00:21:53,870 --> 00:21:58,239
<i>Like a comet,</i>

243
00:21:58,307 --> 00:22:04,405
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

244
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:11,579
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

245
00:22:12,588 --> 00:22:21,963
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

246
00:22:23,299 --> 00:22:30,831
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

247
00:22:30,907 --> 00:22:34,900
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

248
00:22:37,713 --> 00:22:39,203
I never forget my ideal...

249
00:22:39,482 --> 00:22:44,715
to develop the Village Hidden in the Leaf
and protect its people.

250
00:22:45,688 --> 00:22:48,350
The Hokages have sacrificed
their lives for that dream.

251
00:22:49,759 --> 00:22:52,523
And now,
I also will put my life on the line.

252
00:22:53,262 --> 00:22:57,028
From this moment,
I am the Fifth Hokage!

253
00:22:58,034 --> 00:23:02,334
Next time: "The Fifth Hokage!
A Life on the Line!"
